(So that neither side will be hurt.)

299
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,600
(Don't change the subject.)

300
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,039
(Let's all be safe.)

301
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,240
(Why?)

302
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,559
(Just remain peaceful.)

303
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,879
Dear journalists,

