313
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:51,399
(Dear journalists,)

314
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:53,279
(please do not spread rumors.)

315
00:15:53,879 --> 00:15:54,799
Xiu.

316
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,799
Turns out, behind the chemical plant
