He said he's still busy.

334
00:16:43,399 --> 00:16:45,000
Don't you still have me?

335
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,399
It's different.

336
00:16:50,039 --> 00:16:51,759
That's okay.

337
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:54,320
Dad said he would give me a gift.

338
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,840
Give him some time.

339
00:16:56,519 --> 00:16:57,359
A gift?

340
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,279
What gift?

341
00:16:59,759 --> 00:17:01,159
It's a secret.

342
00:17:07,645 --> 00:17:12,736
♪Anyway, everyone knows their roles♪

343
00:17:18,799 --> 00:17:20,000
I'm off to work.

