347
00:17:34,119 --> 00:17:35,480
(yet memory)

348
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:38,279
(reminds us)

349
00:17:38,279 --> 00:17:40,920
(that such tranquility was hard-won.)

350
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,720
(It needs to be cherished)

351
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,759
(and requires fighting.)

352
00:17:44,759 --> 00:17:47,880
(Even a hero is needed to stand up.)

353
00:17:53,359 --> 00:17:54,359
Fresh milk.

354
00:17:59,581 --> 00:18:01,504
(Loyalty)

355
00:18:01,759 --> 00:18:02,599
Morning.

356
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,320
Okay.

357
00:18:05,277 --> 00:18:07,408
♪Life is like a play♪

358
00:18:10,653 --> 00:18:15,470
