359
00:18:19,581 --> 00:18:24,238
♪You can't tell what he's laughing at♪

360
00:18:30,560 --> 00:18:31,400
Qi.

361
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:32,240
Morning.

362
00:18:39,839 --> 00:18:43,279
(Perhaps, in the end, the hero's name
will be forgotten.)

363
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:46,160
(But we will always remember)

364
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:49,359
(that this seemingly ordinary
and peaceful life)

365
00:18:49,359 --> 00:18:51,440
(was never taken for granted.)

366
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:55,119
(Chen Tianshuang.)

367
00:18:55,799 --> 00:18:57,640
(No matter where you are,)

368
00:18:57,640 --> 00:19:00,000
(Lian'an Town and I want to thank you.)

369
00:19:00,599 --> 00:19:02,079
(And I believe)

370
00:19:02,519 --> 00:19:04,119
